title: Bug 121170 - getColumnLabel() returns different results before and after data extraction
description: When calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before and after data extraction, the results differ.
OB: When calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction, it returns empty strings for some columns.
EB: When calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction, it should return user recognizable strings for all columns.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Before extracting data, call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() for multiple columns.
2. Observe that some columns return empty strings instead of user recognizable labels.
